sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Intersect ENT, Inc. (Symbol: XENT), where a total volume of 2,010 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 201,000 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 58% of XENT's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 346,500 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $20 strike call option expiring November 15, 2019, with 1,000 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 100,000 underlying shares of XENT.
